description: Last year he brought her a Sybian which she rides all day and night. This year she has a big surprise for Santa. After his cookies and milk, he will fall asleep on the floor. She will drag him to her bed and when he wakes up, Santa’s Big Cock will be deep down her throat, like a candy cane. She has been a bad girl, BUT SHE CAN GET A MONSTER LOAD OF PRESENTS FROM SANTA.
title: SANTA'S BIG LOAD
